name: Alan Moore Portrait 1 Print - signed by Alan Moore
description:
Alan Moore Portrait Limited Edition Print signed by Alan Moore and Lee Burrows.  These 2010 portraits were painted by the Northampton artist Lee Burrows (www.leeburrowsart.com) who became friends with Alan after working on youth and community projects in the Spring Boroughs area of Northampton.
The prints are a limited edition of 50.  The original oil painting titled "Alan Moore 2" is owned by the man himself.
